Package com.foley.graph.core

Class BasicHashGraph<V,​E>

java.lang.Object
com.foley.graph.core.AbstractGraph<V,​E>
com.foley.graph.core.BasicHashGraph<V,​E>
Type Parameters:
V - The type of vertices in the graph
E - The type of cost between vertices in the graph
All Implemented Interfaces:
Graph<V,​E>
public class BasicHashGraph<V,​E> extends AbstractGraph<V,​E> implements Graph<V,​E>
A basic implementation of a graph that uses a hash map as the backing data structure for the edges connecting vertices. This implementation does not allow for multiple edges of differing cost between vertices
